Kerima (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kerima_(actress) 0 Kerima (born February 10, 1925) was an actress best known for her role in Outcast of the Islands. Although commonly believed to be Algerian as she was portrayed when she gained fame as an actress, she is actually French.
